{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-jsx","path":"/Neovim/05-vim-airline/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"b8c44184-57eb-50ab-ada8-ce84e33a1faa","html":"<h2>Plugin Airline and Airline themes</h2>\n<p>Add the following to <code class=\"language-text\">~/.config/nvim/vim-plug/plugins.vim</code></p>\n<code-fence lang=\"null\" null>\n    <textarea vue-slot=\"code\">\n      Plug 'vim-airline/vim-airline'\nPlug 'vim-airline/vim-airline-themes'\n    </textarea>\n    </code-fence>\n  \n<h2>Create config</h2>\n<p>Create theme file for airline</p>\n<code-fence lang=\"null\" null>\n    <textarea vue-slot=\"code\">\n      touch ~/.config/nvim/themes/airline.vim\n    </textarea>\n    </code-fence>\n  \n<p>Add the following configuration</p>\n<code-fence lang=\"null\" null>\n    <textarea vue-slot=\"code\">\n      \" enable tabline\nlet g:airline#extensions#tabline#enabled = 1\nlet g:airline#extensions#tabline#left_sep = ''\nlet g:airline#extensions#tabline#left_alt_sep = ''\nlet g:airline#extensions#tabline#right_sep = ''\nlet g:airline#extensions#tabline#right_alt_sep = ''\n\n\" enable powerline fonts\nlet g:airline_powerline_fonts = 1\nlet g:airline_left_sep = ''\nlet g:airline_right_sep = ''\n\n\" Switch to your current theme\nlet g:airline_theme = 'onedark'\n\n\" Always show tabs\nset showtabline=2\n\n\" We don't need to see things like -- INSERT -- anymore\nset noshowmode\n    </textarea>\n    </code-fence>\n  \n<p>Don't forget to source this file</p>\n<code-fence lang=\"null\" null>\n    <textarea vue-slot=\"code\">\n      source $HOME/.config/nvim/themes/airline.vim\n    </textarea>\n    </code-fence>\n  \n<h2>Install fonts</h2>\n<p>You may want to install these fonts if you want the little arrows and stuff</p>\n<code-fence lang=\"null\" null>\n    <textarea vue-slot=\"code\">\n      # clone\ngit clone https://github.com/powerline/fonts.git --depth=1\n# install\ncd fonts\n./install.sh\n# clean-up a bit\ncd ..\nrm -rf fonts\n    </textarea>\n    </code-fence>\n  \n<h2>Further documentation and repo</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/vim-airline/vim-airline\">vim airline</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/vim-airline/vim-airline-themes\">vim airline themes</a></p>","excerpt":"Plugin Airline and Airline themes Add the following to  Create config Create theme file for airline Add the following configuration Don'tâ€¦","frontmatter":{"title":"Airline","tags":["neovim"],"image":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/ff1c356d6a7f46604822f50919abcf83/a8734/neovim.png"},"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":3.456140350877193,"src":"/static/ff1c356d6a7f46604822f50919abcf83/5134e/neovim.png","srcSet":"/static/ff1c356d6a7f46604822f50919abcf83/06f82/neovim.png 197w,\n/static/ff1c356d6a7f46604822f50919abcf83/da7d7/neovim.png 393w,\n/static/ff1c356d6a7f46604822f50919abcf83/5134e/neovim.png 786w,\n/static/ff1c356d6a7f46604822f50919abcf83/31987/neovim.png 1000w","sizes":"(max-width: 786px) 100vw, 786px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Neovim/05-vim-airline/","prev":{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/Neovim/06-file-explorer/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Exploring coc-explorer","tags":["neovim"]}}},"next":{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/Neovim/04-vim-coc/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Neovim Intellisense with coc","tags":["neovim"]}}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864"]}